text: Kamel Ali El-Sayed (born 13 May 1935) is an Egyptian wrestler. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Egypt Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Cairo
